title: DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 9 Awards Presented
text:
DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 9 Awards Presented Published: October 20, 2015 Print Lazarius Patterson, Andy DeGraw, Coach Kevin Creasy 
Oakland's 43-14 win over rival Riverdale in week 9 of the prep football season makes the Patriots' the DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS "Game of the Week" award recipient. 
Andy DeGraw, Vice President of DIRECTV by EnterSource, presented a plaque Tuesday. 
The game's MVP was running back Lazarius Patterson. The junior rushed for 243-yards and three touchdowns in Oakland's win over Riverdale. Just the week before, versus Haywood, he had four touchdowns. Related Articles
